{"tid":2319453,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《TENET天能》12月15日hmvod上架 將加推3D版","createTime":"2020-12-10T06:08:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T06:18:48.000Z","uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2f1c57d8caa40454d776b25f073b1bfb96feb21f","tid":2319453,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T06:08:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201209/S2RPS2WHOREULMEBOK3A47MELU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201209%2FS2RPS2WHOREULMEBOK3A47MELU%2F&d=DJHqE1tJ5F0S1%2BmpD1KYprZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=4eb545c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201209%2FS2RPS2WHOREULMEBOK3A47MELU%2F&h=06cc7d68\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201209/S2RPS2WHOREULMEBOK3A47MELU/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《TENET天能》將於12月15日在本土平台hmvod上映。在聖誕期間，觀眾更可以換上全新技術製作的電話保護貼，以肉眼享受3D電影效果。<br />\n<br />\n據知，該3D保護貼平時與一般保護貼無異，並不會影響電話正常使用，不需反覆拆除及重貼。不過由於技術新穎，目前3D保護貼只支援iPhone12及iPhone12 Pro。<br />\n<br />\n平台目前已上載有「裸眼3D」效果的合共16部電影，包括《復仇者聯盟3: 無限之戰》、《復仇者聯盟4: 終局之戰》、《魔雪奇緣2》、《獅子王》、《少年PI的奇幻漂流》、《迷你兵團》、《玉蒲團3D》、《阿凡達》、《侏羅紀世界》、《水行俠》、《末日先鋒：戰甲飛車》、《玉蒲團之偷情寶鑑》、《英雄本色》、《鐵達尼號》、《神奇女俠》及《哈利波特：神秘的魔法石》。<br />\n<br />\n本土串流平台hmvod推出3D電話保護貼，無需任何其他幫助即可肉眼睇3D效果。<br />\n本土串流平台hmvod推出3D電話保護貼，無需任何其他幫助即可肉眼睇3D效果。<br />\n-----------------------------"},{"pid":"7e902815a0f878978921f989ded7db6e48002f44","tid":2319453,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T06:09:15.000Z","msg":"Nolan知道佢心血竟然出3D版會唔會嘔血㗎"},{"pid":"a0d422638c74a4444500ce80447ee65b04cf06ff","tid":2319453,"uid":83328,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T06:09:37.000Z","msg":"想激死Nolan<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢最憎3D電影<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb770b87e47203b72662845805a88b1193747c84","tid":2319453,"uid":19867,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T06:18:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TrAyPHz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTrAyPHz.jpg&h=7ed60477&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}